{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-14525/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-14525"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:45:25"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["plan américain"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["high"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Lighting"]},"value":{"none":["backlighting"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["group shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man searches a crowded dance hall from an upper balcony as balloons drop."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14525/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-14525","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14525/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-14525"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14525/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14525/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14525/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14525/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14525/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14525/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14525/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14525/canvas/1/c49f1b7f-7d3c-4e7f-a1dd-365e5f35e82d","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-02T20:09:19.744Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>While many of PTA’s films frame central characters marginally, <em>Phantom Thread</em> mostly avoids this tactic. This shot is a notable exception: Reynolds is a silhouette on the edge of the brightly-coloredframe, further emphasizing his sense of obscurity and exclusion.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14525/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:315.6195262738852,267.3800756369426,305.4697452229299,747.0143312101911"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14525/canvas/1/8facbd38-6fb7-4151-a990-7ddd8242f44a","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-02T20:09:41.578Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The casual racism of the era that Lady Baltimore exhibits at the dinner where Reynolds and Alma fight over their backgammon game can also be seen at the party. A Confederate flag passes in the background, and revelers wear Native American costumes.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14525/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1303.0623009554142,439.54269506369417,110.7354697452231,100.12141719745233"}}}]}]}]}